    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example is mechanically robust, having undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive valve clearance adjustment. The chassis integrity is confirmed with a reinforced rear subframe, mitigating common floor-pan fatigue. Power is delivered through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, providing exceptional lateral grip and predictable oversteer characteristics. The suspension retains its sharp response with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals are optimized for spirited use, offering a pure analog driving experience with precise throttle response via its individual throttle bodies.",
